    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/be5242424ddb5d09557ea36744dd751e.webp?t=1731933059\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><br>一半人类，一半恶魔，沉迷于复仇而无法自拔。化身“无名”，勇闯险恶无比的幽冥疆域。摧毁恶魔军团及其头领，做好准备与赤焰判官展开一场史诗对决。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/920348ca23d5869941807dc8f792c01f.poster.avif?t=1731933059\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/920348ca23d5869941807dc8f792c01f.webm?t=1731933059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/920348ca23d5869941807dc8f792c01f.mp4?t=1731933059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/49084a0f9f6599fc01a253e9559c3d77.webp?t=1731933059\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>《Metal:Hellsinger》 是一款节奏感十足的第一人称射击游戏，你可以随着节拍射击，获得更加震撼的游戏体验。你的杀戮与音乐节奏越同步，音乐就会变得越激昂，你造成的破坏也越大。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/ab473ee6e3e3ae67238bead0a88247ee.webp?t=1731933059\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>你可以用一柄颅骨剑或各种极具杀伤力的枪对抗恶魔军团。每种武器都有各自的终极技能，例如“乌鸦杀手”或“决别”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/6033fd36f4bf0adf2c310bbe679dc5a2.webp?t=1731933059\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>试玩一段史诗般的剧情，旁白由著名获奖演员Troy Baker全情演绎。解锁特别挑战，征服炼狱挑战各个位面，在各关卡中不断变强，登上排行榜高位。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/27e75751cbd6690ed6327e886641b467.poster.avif?t=1731933059\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/27e75751cbd6690ed6327e886641b467.webm?t=1731933059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/27e75751cbd6690ed6327e886641b467.mp4?t=1731933059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/9c08ea97bb66b9dd184864c7c8b9144c.webp?t=1731933059\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>尽管冥界通常被称为地狱，但它其实是上千个地狱的融合体，所有这些地狱都各有恐怖和残酷之处。为了推翻赤焰判官的统治，你必须一路奋战，穿越最凶险的角落，从冰冷的Voke 界一直到疯狂的 Stygia 界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/2eafb4624b637a6eb6033c9a6ee2c710.webp?t=1731933059\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>《Metal:Hellsinger》 由 The Outsiders 的资深第一人称射击游戏团队打造，是 《Payday 2》 游戏总监以及 《Battlefield 3》 和《Battlefield: Bad Company 2》首席设计师David Goldfarb的倾力之作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/7a22ad096085502a8b008a59d1a7735c.webp?t=1731933059\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>游戏中的每一首歌曲均由作曲家二人组Two Feathers专门为本游戏创作，并由Serj Tankian（System of a Down乐队）、Randy Blythe（Lamb of God乐队）和Alissa White-Gluz（Arch Enemy乐队）等一众金属乐大咖倾情演绎！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061910/extras/4fae3d551cde6bd7a0fc121d87b7ccb4.avif?t=1731933059\" width=616 height=702 /></span><br><br><strong>DMCA及版权信息：</strong><br>游戏中的歌曲均专门为我们的游戏编写、制作和演绎，版权完全归我方所有。我们已尽一切努力来确保内容创作者不会因为侵权而收到版权警示。",
